  "short_description": "High-performance 100Gbps direct attach copper cable with QSFP28 connectors, 3m length.",
  "description": "The Ubiquiti UACC-DAC-QSFP28-3M is a high-performance direct attach cable designed to facilitate seamless connections between devices equipped with QSFP28 and QSFP+ interfaces. Measuring 3 meters in length, this cable supports data transfer rates of up to 100 Gbps, making it an ideal solution for high-bandwidth applications that require rapid data transmission over short distances.",
  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "High-Speed Connectivity",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti UACC-DAC-QSFP28-3M is a high-performance direct attach cable designed to facilitate seamless connections between devices equipped with QSFP28 and QSFP+ interfaces. Measuring 3 meters in length, this cable supports data transfer rates of up to 100 Gbps, making it an ideal solution for high-bandwidth applications that require rapid data transmission over short distances. Its robust design ensures minimal latency and reliable performance, essential for maintaining the efficiency of modern data centers and network infrastructures. The backward compatibility with QSFP+ allows for greater flexibility in deployment, ensuring smooth integration into existing network environments."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Durable Construction",
      "text": "Constructed with a 30 AWG gauge and featuring a durable PVC jacket, the UACC-DAC-QSFP28-3M is built to withstand the demands of intensive networking environments. The cable's black PVC sheath has an outer diameter of 7 mm and a minimum bend radius of 37 mm, offering flexibility without compromising structural integrity. It operates efficiently within a temperature range of 0°C to 70°C, ensuring consistent performance under varying environmental conditions. The cable's maximum power consumption is rated at 2.5W, reflecting its energy-efficient design."
    }
  ],
